76
0:03:15.178,000 --> 0:03:17,000
in America is Portland, Oregon.

77
0:03:17.589,000 --> 0:03:2,000
Portland made a bunch of decisions in the 1970s

78
0:03:20.928,000 --> 0:03:21,000
that began to distinguish it

79
0:03:22.626,000 --> 0:03:24,000
