126
0:05:14.489,000 --> 0:05:15,000
than most other states,

127
0:05:15.829,000 --> 0:05:16,000
which may be a good thing or a bad thing,

128
0:05:17.394,000 --> 0:05:18,000
but it makes you glad they're driving less.

129
0:05:19.393,000 --> 0:05:21,000
(Laughter)

130
0:05:21.766,000 --> 0:05:24,000
