168
0:06:59.479,000 --> 0:07:02,000
fully one third of all children born after 2000

169
0:07:03.276,000 --> 0:07:04,000
will get diabetes.

170
0:07:04.976,000 --> 0:07:05,000
We have the first generation of children in America

171
0:07:06.949,000 --> 0:07:09,000
