0:07:10.819,000 --> 0:07:12,000
I believe that this American healthcare crisis

173
0:07:13.03,000 --> 0:07:14,000
that we've all heard about

174
0:07:14.468,000 --> 0:07:16,000
is an urban design crisis,

175
0:07:17.084,000 --> 0:07:19,000
