189
0:07:52.854,000 --> 0:07:54,000
between the latter two.

190
0:07:54.902,000 --> 0:07:56,000
Dr. James Levine at, in this case,

191
0:07:56.919,000 --> 0:07:58,000
the aptly-named Mayo Clinic

192
0:07:59.112,000 --> 0:08:03,000
